		<title>狗狗也超愛吃醋？金毛犬對著玩偶生氣讓主人哭笑不得 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/13/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b9%9f%e8%b6%85%e6%84%9b%e5%90%83%e9%86%8b%ef%bc%9f%e9%87%91%e6%af%9b%e7%8a%ac%e5%b0%8d%e8%91%97%e7%8e%a9%e5%81%b6%e7%94%9f%e6%b0%a3%e8%ae%93%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e5%93%ad%e7%ac%91/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 13 Oct 2025 06:07:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
